---
// 客服选择组件
---
<!-- 引入Salesmartly客服插件 -->
<script src="https://plugin-code.salesmartly.com/js/project_420571_432727_1754890534.js"></script>

<div class="customer-service py-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-xl my-10 px-4 md:px-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-blue-400">联系投资顾问</h2>
  <p class="text-center text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    我们的专业投资顾问团队随时为您提供一对一的咨询服务，助您把握投资机会
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
    <!-- 投资顾问 1 - 使用Salesmartly客服 -->
    <div class="advisor-card bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-700/50 hover:shadow-blue-500/20 border border-slate-700">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 relative">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/id/1005/200/200"
          alt="投资顾问张老师"
          class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-blue-500"
        />
        <span class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-800"></span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-1 text-white">张老师</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-blue-400 mb-3">高级投资顾问</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm mb-4">擅长：A股趋势分析、价值投资</p>
      <button
        onclick="window.salesmartly?.showPanel()"
        class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        立即咨询
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- 投资顾问 2 - 预留位置 -->
    <div class="advisor-card bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-700/50 hover:shadow-blue-500/20 border border-slate-700">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 relative">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/id/1012/200/200"
          alt="投资顾问李老师"
          class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-blue-500"
        />
        <span class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-800"></span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-1 text-white">李老师</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-blue-400 mb-3">资深股票分析师</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm mb-4">擅长：技术分析、短线操作</p>
      <button
        class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md transition-colors duration-300"
        disabled
      >
        即将上线
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- 投资顾问 3 - 预留位置 -->
    <div class="advisor-card bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-slate-700/50 hover:shadow-blue-500/20 border border-slate-700">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 relative">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/id/1025/200/200"
          alt="投资顾问王老师"
          class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-blue-500"
        />
        <span class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-5 h-5 bg-gray-500 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-800"></span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-1 text-white">王老师</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-blue-400 mb-3">量化投资专家</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm mb-4">擅长：量化策略、风险管理</p>
      <button
        class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md transition-colors duration-300"
        disabled
      >
        即将上线
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-gray-500 px-4">
    <p>风险提示：投资有风险，入市需谨慎。本平台提供的信息仅供参考，不构成投资建议。</p>
  </div>
</div>